{"tid":1283271,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"[推俾連仔睇] 即ban 所有自殺有關嘅post","createTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T18:25:50.000Z","uid":258170,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"265911c7bf49cf182bd65a9126b2eeb3005fb0b2","tid":1283271,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:02.000Z","msg":"屌，見到嗰啲自殺post 就把撚鬼火。自殺係好令人關注，但係post出嚟會有連鎖效應㗎，叫werther effect(維基)。<br />\n<br />\n連登係香港一大social media，有好多人會去睇。我喺度要求連仔，要求各位巴絲，係時候盡返下責任，ban下呢啲post，見到唔好推，唔好再俾呢種自殺行為繼續落去。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同我一人一推，推到連仔見到為止。</span></span>"},{"pid":"75dc1e149db368c6d118c02fc98d0ca6f65a307a","tid":1283271,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:21.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"9e4eedc98df7a5453013a37db68dd5cba4adb811","tid":1283271,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:34.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"bfd2e211d1b6e765fa430feadf02e750da69edef","tid":1283271,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:44.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"8367f16492b8d2eec359b832d0f54b8bee4aa261","tid":1283271,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:14:54.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"69eb231b135c2be9ba75b61ffc892d7f8f197cf2","tid":1283271,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:15:04.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"caac995b87bb79ee4fe7668486d744e3c49c17f9","tid":1283271,"uid":258170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T18:15:55.000Z","msg":"補番維基link：<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Copycat_suicide\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FCopycat_suicide&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=a4b8722c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Copycat_suicide